/-!

### B.11. Reduce member of `FluxesFive.elemsNoExotics`

-/

lemma reduce_mem_elemsNoExotics {F : FiveQuanta 𝓩}
    (hx : F.toFluxesFive ∈ FluxesFive.elemsNoExotics) :
    F.reduce.toFluxesFive ∈ FluxesFive.elemsNoExotics := by
